  "prompt": "I am already using Reliance Jio SIM card. How to check data usage on the same ?",
  "response": "To check your data usage on a Reliance Jio SIM card, you have several options:\n\n1. MyJio Mobile App\n- Download MyJio app from Play Store/App Store\n- Open the app\n- Log in with your Jio mobile number\n- Check data usage under \"My Plan\" or \"Usage\"\n\n2. Dial USSD Code\n- Dial *444# from your Jio SIM\n- Select option to view data usage\n- Receive usage details via SMS\n\n3. SMS Method\n- Send SMS \"DATA\" to 141\n- Receive data usage details on your phone\n\n4. Jio Website\n- Visit www.jio.com\n- Log in to your account\n- Check data usage in account section\n\n5. Customer Care\n- Call 199\n- Ask customer care representative about your data usage\n\n6. Jio Customer Care App\n- Download \"MyJio Care\" app\n- Log in with your details\n- Check data usage and other account information\n\nThese methods will help you track your current data consumption quickly and easily.",
